snippet.textDisplay:
This one day I was out since morning. First university, then work and then some shopping. After I left from shopping, I was feeling dull and lonely since it had been a sorta long day on my own. I get home, open my phone and the first notification I see is a Snapchat text from her saying, “Where have you been all day?” This 6 letter text literally made me feel so much better and made my mood better. I felt I mattered. 

Sadly her parents married her off to another guy as they wanted a settled 26-27 year old guy with an MBA. And here we are
